		<guid isPermaLink="false">http://kimbeasley.com/?p=2272</guid>
		<description>HERE&amp;#8217;S TO ADMINISTRATIVE ASSISTANTS! WE THANK YOU FOR ALL THAT YOU DO! It&amp;#8217;s Administrative Assistant&amp;#8217;s Day! It&amp;#8217;s time to celebrate those assistants that help our businesses run smoothly each and every day. Today&amp;#8217;s administrative professionals wear many hats. They are no longer just a secretary or a receptionist; they are more than an executive assistant. [...]</description>
			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<!-- Start Shareaholic LikeButtonSetTop Automatic --><!-- End Shareaholic LikeButtonSetTop Automatic --><p style="text-align: center;"><strong>HERE&#8217;S TO ADMINISTRATIVE ASSISTANTS! WE THANK YOU FOR ALL THAT YOU DO!</strong></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://kimbeasley.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/thank-you.jpg"><img class="aligncenter" title="thank-you" src="http://kimbeasley.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/thank-you-300x228.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="228" /></a></p>
<p>It&#8217;s Administrative Assistant&#8217;s Day! It&#8217;s time to celebrate those assistants that help our businesses run smoothly each and every day. Today&#8217;s administrative professionals wear many hats. They are no longer just a secretary or a receptionist; they are more than an executive assistant. They are the face and voice that is on the front line of the business each and every day. They are the one that most of your customers may deal with.</p>
<p>Today is a day to give thanks to these professionals for the countless hours they put in for you and your business. There are many ways to celebrate these unique individuals. First and foremost the most important thing is to just say &#8220;thank you&#8221;. Let them know how much they mean to you and your business and how much you appreciate all that they do.</p>
<p>In addition you can thank them in many ways including:</p>
<ul>
<li>Sending them flowers.</li>
<li>Taking them out to breakfast or lunch.</li>
<li>Hosting an in-office breakfast or luncheon in their honor.</li>
<li>Sending them a gift certificate to places like Amazon.com so they can get a great book.</li>
<li>Giving them a gift certificate to their favorite lunch spot.Â </li>
<li>Letting them off early.</li>
</ul>
<p>The possibilities are endless and will vary depending on your business or location but the most important thing is to let them know you appreciate all the hard work that they do for you.</p>
<div id="dprv_cp_v2.02" lang="en" xml:lang="en" class="notranslate" style="vertical-align:baseline; padding: 2px 3px 1px 3px; margin-top:2px; margin-bottom:2px; border-collapse:separate; line-height:12px;float:none; font-family: Tahoma, MS Sans Serif; font-size:13px;border:0px;background:transparent none;display:table;" title="certified 25 April 2012 17:32:31 UTC by Digiprove certificate P278390" ><a href="http://www.digiprove.com/show_certificate.aspx?id=P278390%26guid=8rzDj3_LMk-toBla5_ESZw" target="_blank" rel="copyright" style="height:12px; line-height: 12px; border:0px; padding:0px; margin:0px; float:none; display:inline; text-decoration: none; background:transparent none; line-height:normal; font-family: Tahoma, MS Sans Serif; font-style:normal; font-weight:normal; font-size:9px;"><img src="http://kimbeasley.com/wp-content/plugins/digiproveblog/dp_seal_trans_16x16.png" style="max-width:none !important;width:12px;height:12px;vertical-align:0px; display:inline; border:0px; margin:0px; padding:0px; float:none; background:transparent none" border="0" alt=""/><span style="font-family: Tahoma, MS Sans Serif; font-style:normal; font-size:9px; font-weight:normal; color:#636363; border:0px; float:none; display:inline; text-decoration:none; letter-spacing:normal; padding:0px; padding-left:6px; vertical-align:3px;margin-bottom:3px" onmouseover="this.style.color='#A35353';" onmouseout="this.style.color='#636363';">Copyright&nbsp;secured&nbsp;by&nbsp;Digiprove&nbsp;&copy;&nbsp;2012&nbsp;Kim&nbsp;Beasley</span></a><a title='Click to see details of license' href="javascript:dprv_DisplayLicense('2272')" style="font-family: Tahoma, MS Sans Serif; font-style:normal; display:block; font-size:9px; font-weight:normal; color:#636363; border:0px; float:none; text-align:left; text-decoration:none; letter-spacing:normal; line-height:12px; vertical-align:3px; padding:0px; padding-left:18px;margin-bottom:3px;" onmouseover="this.style.color='#A35353';" onmouseout="this.style.color='#6363