		<title>Boosting Your Business Savvy in 2012</title>
		<link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/SocialMediaMarketingForBusiness/~3/00v6g7aCxtk/</link>
		<comments>http://kimbeasley.com/2012/02/13/boosting-your-business-savvy-in-2012/#comments</comments>
